    ENDIF.


*Billing Plan -> process via BDC VA02 -> must check date format and number
*date format -> yyyy/mm/dd
*number -> no comma(,) and no alphabet
    MOVE-CORRESPONDING CS_QUOTATION TO LS_BILLINGPLAN.
