  method VALIDATE_INPUT.
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*  Program ID         : ZCL_SDSSD_CRET_CHG_QUOT_SRV / VALIDATE_INPUT
*  Creation Date      : 06.06.2024
*  Author             : Zulkiff B. (Eviden)
*  Add-on ID          : ZSDI033
*  Description        : Validate data input from Salesforce
*  Purpose            : Validate Header / Item
*  Copied from        : N/A
*  Restriction        : N/A
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*  CHANGE HISTORY
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*  Date        Task #      Programmer  Description
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------
*  DD.MM.YYYY  TR no.      ABAP Name   Detail
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------

* Initialize Output
    CLEAR: EF_INVALID.

    CASE CS_QUOTATION-FLAG.
      WHEN  SPACE OR 'I'.
        VALIDATE_HEADER_CREATE(
           EXPORTING
             IF_RECORD_MODE    = CS_QUOTATION-FLAG
           IMPORTING
             EF_INVALID        = EF_INVALID
           CHANGING
             CS_QUOTATION      = CS_QUOTATION
             CT_RESPONSE       = CT_RESPONSE
       ).

        IF EF_INVALID = SPACE." No Error
          VALIDATE_ITEM_CREATE(
             EXPORTING
               IF_RECORD_MODE    = CS_QUOTATION-FLAG
             IMPORTING
               EF_INVALID        = EF_INVALID
